channel.title: Comments on: Deimos Fishing – How to Earn Daughter Tokens

item.title: By: Steppin
item.dc:creator: Steppin
item.description: Great guide, thank you for your work. I noticed that there is one fish missing from your list though. It is the Aquapulmo, It’s found during vome, and requires processed Vass residue.
